text-gray-600 rounded-full px-3 py-1","children":"customer support"}],["$","span","AI automation",{"className":"text-xs font-mono bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 rounded-full px-3 py-1","children":"AI automation"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose-goated","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Customer support is one of the largest operating costs for growing businesses. A 50-person company spends $500k+ per year answering the same questions repeatedly."}]]}],["$","p","1",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"AI chatbots are not the future of support anymore. They are here now, and the ones doing it right are cutting support costs by 40% while actually improving customer satisfaction."}]]}],["$","h2","2",{"className":"font-serif text-2xl text-dark mt-12 mb-4","children":"The State of AI Chatbots in 2026"}],["$","p","3",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Five years ago, chatbots were bad. They could barely understand what you were asking and offered zero real value."}]]}],["$","p","4",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Today is completely different. Modern AI models can handle nuanced language, understand context, and provide genuinely helpful responses. When trained on your specific knowledge base, they solve most common customer problems without human intervention."}]]}],["$","h2","5",{"className":"font-serif text-2xl text-dark mt-12 mb-4","children":"How Much Can Chatbots Really Handle?"}],["$","p","6",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Based on real deployments we have built at GOATED., here is what the data shows:"}]]}],["$","li","7",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed ml-5 mb-2 list-disc","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"First contact resolution:"}],["$","span","2",{"children":" 60-70% of customer questions are completely resolved by the chatbot"}]]}],["$","li","8",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed ml-5 mb-2 list-disc","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"Escalation rate:"}],["$","span","2",{"children":" 20-30% of questions are partially answered and escalated to a human with full context already attached"}]]}],["$","li","9",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed ml-5 mb-2 list-disc","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","children":"Out-of-scope:"}],["$","span","2",{"children":" 5-10% of questions are completely outside the chatbot's knowledge and routed directly to support"}]]}],["$","p","10",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"The result is that your support team spends their time on genuinely complex issues instead of answering \"What is your return policy?\" for the 1000th time."}]]}],["$","h2","11",{"className":"font-serif text-2xl text-dark mt-12 mb-4","children":"Types of Chatbots Worth Building"}],["$","h3","12",{"className":"font-sans text-lg font-semibold text-dark mt-8 mb-3","children":"1. FAQ Bots"}],["$","p","13",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":"Simple but effective. These understand questions about common topics (pricing, shipping, returns, hours) and provide instant answers."}]]}],["$","p","14",{"className":"font-sans text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","span","0",{"children":""}],["$","strong","1",{"className":"font-semibold text-dark","chi